Control Smoker tongue drag damage and interval.

-L4D2 original code-
https://github.com/Attano/L4D2-Competitive-Framework/blob/master/addons/sourcemod/scripting/l4d2_smoker_drag_damage_interval.sp

-ConVar-
"tongue_drag_damage_interval", "1.0", "How often the drag does damage."
"tongue_drag_first_damage_interval", "1.0", "First drag damage interval."
"tongue_drag_first_damage", "3.0", "First drag damage."